Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.83,0:00:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Rin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rin! Come on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yukio still hasn't come back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn Four-Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't come home and doesn't even bother to call...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.51,0:02:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Okumura!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.55,0:02:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There was that hostage incident two days ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They've called in the principal to take responsibility for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the Academy is closed for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't even enter the school buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Izumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The leaders of the Vatican have been replaced and a new pope was elected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it have anything to do with the dismissal of the principal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, things here are gonna change a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just with the Exorcist cram school but the whole Order as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:51.53,Default,,0,0,30,,The Exorcist cram school and the Japanese Branch as a whole
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:55.78,Default,,0,0,30,,have been placed under direct control of the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:03:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please welcome the new Head of the Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the newly assigned Head of the Japanese Branch, Yukio Okumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Professor Okumura...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still a student...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the same Middle First Class as I.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to accepting the position of the Branch leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I have also received the title of Paladin as of today.{FUCKING LOL}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I request your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Yukio is the new Paladin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And also Head of the Japanese Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what this new pope is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, he got ahead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be the first to become Paladin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is {\i1}that{\i0\fscx140} {\r}your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever gotten even close to my level?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really the new Paladin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the title of the strongest Exorcist, just like Father had.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my little brother and I know that you work your ass off when no one's looking,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but why didn't you tell me something this important?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an urgent summon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then at least send me an e-mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I will do that next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason I've been appointed Paladin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is so I could carry out the plan of the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My people! Our whole history we have lived in fear of the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But that shall end today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as the light of civilization drove away the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we shall drive away all the demons from this world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and return Assiah to the hands of humankind once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I, Pope Ernst, hereby order all Exorcists around the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:05:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Begin Operation Jacob's Ladder!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Jacob's Ladder"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I am responsible for carrying out that plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll help us too, won't you Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off to a meeting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Demon slayer weapons developed by the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes the power of the defeated demon and boosts your Exorcism.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When I hold this in my hand I feel like fighting too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima, it's not a toy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to be Tamers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then use that grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll rather stick with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Although you're permitted to carry arms, you still lack experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful not to get in the way of other Exorcists.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"O Sylphs born of the dark mist. gather in the lands of honey and milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Spread your crystalline wings and dance in the sky!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:06:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well! We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This... is so one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rin! Is this what Exorcists do?{from preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To me it feels we're...{from preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:08:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We have already completed cleansing 443 556 regions,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but we're facing resistance in a number of other regions...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell every single Exorcist that this is a Crusade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Without sacrifices our dreams will never come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Is there something you'd like to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will you turn Rin back to human?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that even possible?{\i0}{mfw he's buying this shit}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Kurikara has sealed Rin's blue flames into Gehenna.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The human world of Assiah and the demon world of Gehenna{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are like the two sides of a mirror.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we destroy Gehenna as a whole, all demonic power will be gone,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Rin will return to an ordinary human.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's impossible...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's impossible to destroy Gehenna.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it is possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have spent 15 years to develop the ultimate weapon, the Messiah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Messiah can be launched anytime on my command,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but the Gehenna Gate needs to be opened first.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Gehenna Gate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It literally is a gate in space-time between Assiah and Gehenna.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is believed that only Satan can open it, but we managed to create an artificial one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To maintain the Gate for a longer time, we need immense amounts of demon blood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can Rin really become human again if we destroy Gehenna?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only Rin, but you as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did you think I'm not aware of your secret, my grandson?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys, what are you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,These are our rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We got yours too while there were some left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rin, me too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you'll get some too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you even think about eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiemi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A boar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukio...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You will pay for this, humans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:11:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You hurt my kin... We have protected this forest for over 2000 years!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the Lord of this forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Yukio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? I'm hunting demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the Lord of this forest! He was just angry because we killed his kin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I am ordered to eliminate every demon from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Every?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Blackie and Ukobach and Izumo's Gods of Harvest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you're gonna kill {\i1}them{\i0\fscx140} {\r}too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Just as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We must get rid of every single demon.{FUCKING PATHETIC}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{CM}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to kill every demon there is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Exorcists are {\i1}not{\i0\fscx140} {\r}butchers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I said let go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i0}What did you do to him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Blackie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okumura speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bourguignon.{lolfrench -I'll just call him "beefcake" if he turns up again} Take Rin Okumura to the Vatican Headquarters immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:31.96,Default,,0,0,25,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:34.11,Default,,0,0,25,,You said the checkups all returned negative!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that all a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If this plan succeeds we all will be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the authority to lock you up too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Scaredy Four-Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloodsucker weapons? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}'s a type o' demon swords that be suckin' human blood.{dialectify her lines}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I check'd the photo ye sent me 'n' it seems t' have been possess'd by a certain count in Transylvania.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are they making us use this kinda stuff?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes ye think I'd know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, jus' try t' use 'em as lil' as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Sorry I called so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This shit just doesn't feel right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Bon, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To the young professor's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in charge of this so if I ask he should tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,As if he'd tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better look for a more talkative professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Talkative?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Professor Tsubaki?{ah konekochan}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mephisto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the lowest level of the Vatican Headquarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and this prison is often called the Cocytus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It surprises me greatly to meet you here.{lol hamaimon}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{If it pleases you, would you}Pray tell me the details of how you ended up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Okumura as Paladin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And he engaged in a demon hunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is most fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So why are you locked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eins, zwei, drei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened 500 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Johann Faust, was immersed in the most advanced branch of science of the time, artificial life research.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally can't see the resemblance...{That's below the level of talking about similarities... -refering to the "drawings"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your comments to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Vatican forbid every aspect of creating life,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:16:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I left my laboratory to my students,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but apparently they continued my line of research.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.{when he says "hai~" in this tone I just imagine an <3 after it, I can't help it}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The laboratory is located in Poland.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Neuhaus is the student of my student's student, and so on and so forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec. Professor Neuhaus said that someone revived his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Most likely that someone set a trap for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who dislikes me, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the important information.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It is about time I take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse. Can you not hear the bells signaling the start of the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention to miss a moment of this wonderful show.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, if I may beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! You damn clown! I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Eminence, Mephisto has...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Auguste.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Bourguignon are to bolster the defence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No one may interrupt the ceremony we will be performing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As you command.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Now that I meet you in person I see the resemblance to Yuri is even greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Ernst Frederik Egin. Nice to meet you, my grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okumura got sentenced to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:18:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He was supposed to be kept safe until the Exorcist Authorization Exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah well, the Headquarters are in chaos as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We are waiting for Branch Head Okumura's commands as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And where is Rin now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know that, but I heard the execution will be carried out at the top of the True Cross Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,None shall pass here alive.{what is the airspeed of a laden swallow?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ecce lignum crucis in quo salus mundi pependit... venite adoremus}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the wood of the cross on which hung the Saviour of the world... Come let us worship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Popule meus, quid feci tibi?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ye people: what have I made you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Aut in quo contristavi te? Responde mihi.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,or in what have I offended you? Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Agios O Theos; Sanctus Deus}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,O Sacred God,{they say it in greek and then latin}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Agios ischyrós, Sanctus fortis}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,O Strong saint,{same}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Agios athánatos, eleison imas}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sanctus immortalis, miserere nobis.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,O Immortal saint, have mercy on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ecce lignum crucis in quo salus mundi pependit...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the wood of the cross on which hung the Saviour of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,O blood of pitiful demon! Show us the Gates of Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to your stations right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan is being carried out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they executing Okumura? He hasn't done anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For the kin of Satan just being alive is a sin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what the Order of the True Cross calls justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The orders of the Vatican are absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you intend to oppose me, I shall strike you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Shura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:21:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad you side with the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it. I just can't stand the shine of your bald head.{i just don't like your way of doing stuff}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't disappoint me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up you baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing to Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sacrificing him to open the Gehenna Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You lied!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised that you'd turn him human again, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin is a human sacrifice.{Good morning, Yukio!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He will be remembered forever as the hero who destroyed Gehenna!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{FINALLY THE FUCKING ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.60,0:23:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.87,0:23:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the Gehenna Gate opened the way for Armageddon!{on the Hill of Megiddo}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.91,0:23:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Satan! The King of Demons shall burn Hell itself with those flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.81,0:24:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,These brothers are like the two sides of a mirror.{the same simile as earlier}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.00,0:24:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Had he not drawn the Demon-Slaying Blade that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.56,0:24:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,their fate would have been different.
