Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:08.99,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(270,0)}I'm lightly fluttering in wondrous light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:13.08,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(0,440)}like a dancing butterfly in midair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:17.08,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(270,500)}Is this place in another world?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:21.96,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(140,820)}My fall isn't slowing down so
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.75,0:22:25.01,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(220,480)}cut the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:28.22,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(250,0)}Cut the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.22,0:22:29.97,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The numbers that make my head spin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.97,0:22:31.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(0,230)}are forming a rising spiral
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:35.31,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}and there I notice a terrible error.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:39.10,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Connecting people to one another
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:42.61,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}is a shining pale indigo blue wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:46.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's beautiful like a thread of silk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.57,0:22:50.74,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wonder if it's what they call the chains of fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.74,0:22:54.03,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You seek for it and yet you're already caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.03,0:22:55.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}so don't try to struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:58.16,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What is wired life?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.16,0:23:01.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You're a beautiful fool in
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:03.92,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}the way you get entwined in this
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.92,0:23:05.71,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}wired life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.71,0:23:09.09,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You seek for it and yet you're already caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.09,0:23:11.01,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}so don't try to struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:13.22,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What is wired life?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:16.64,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You're a beautiful fool in
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.64,0:23:18.98,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}the way you get entwined in it.
